##If you want to stay up to 1 year

You may be eligible for a [Temporary Worker - Creative and Sporting visa (T5)](https://www.gov.uk/temporary-worker-creative-and-sporting-visa).

###Eligibility

The eligibility criteria include:

+ having a job offer
+ being endorsed by your sport's governing body - you must make a significant contribution to your sport at the highest level

###How long you can stay

You can stay up to 1 year in the UK on this visa. If you want to stay longer you must switch to another type of visa.
